     Date: March 2, 2026
================================================================================

  This document contains complete brand identities for our Final 5 app
  names. Each includes: origin story, brand narrative, taglines, mottos,
  punchlines, ad lines for Gen Z / Gen Alpha / Enterprise / Industries,
  TikTok-ready copy, mascot concepts, sonic branding, hashtag campaigns,
  cultural analysis, and audience-specific positioning.

  All brand stories are built on our app's 111 features including:
    - Multi-channel social reminders (WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, SMS)
    - 60+ daily content categories (Mahabharata, Stan Lee, Stoicism, anime)
    - Ghost Mode & anti-overwhelm (Decision Roulette, Time Debt Tracker)
    - Energy Flow Engine (biometric throttling, cortisol mapping)
    - AI Personas (Drill Sergeant, Therapist, CEO modes)
    - 12+ industry modes (Legal, Healthcare, Dev, Education, Families)
    - Gamification (XP, streaks, leaderboards, real-money stakes)
    - 70 features NOBODY else has + 41 done better than competitors


