                     #2  U N J Y N X  (Score: 90/100)

################################################################################
################################################################################

  Say it:    "Un-jinx" (crystal clear, everyone knows it)
  Meaning:   Remove the jinx/curse of forgetting.
  Letters:   6
  Vibe:      Mystical, empowering, emotionally compelling, magical

================================================================================
  THE ORIGIN STORY
================================================================================

  You know that feeling.

  The birthday you forgot AGAIN. The deadline that slipped through
  AGAIN. The gym session you skipped AGAIN. That promise you made
  and broke AGAIN. It is not laziness. It is not stupidity.

  It is a jinx.

  An invisible curse that makes good people drop the ball on the
  things that matter most. And every to-do app on the market treats
  you like the problem. More lists. More reminders. More guilt.

  UNJYNX takes a different approach: the problem is not YOU. The
  problem is the CURSE. And every curse has a counter-spell.

  UNJYNX is that counter-spell. Built by METAminds, it wraps around
  your life like a protective enchantment. AI that reads your energy
  and knows when to surface a task and when to let you rest. Ghost
  Mode when the world is too loud. Decision Roulette when you are
  paralyzed. A morning message on WhatsApp with a Bhagavad Gita
  verse and your three most important tasks. A Telegram nudge that
  says "your future self is counting on you."

  Other apps add pressure. UNJYNX removes the curse.

  The jinx was real. The cure is UNJYNX.

