    "Break the forgetting curse."

  ALTERNATES:
    "Curse? Broken."
    "Never jinxed again."
    "The anti-jinx for your life."
    "Your tasks were cursed. Now they're cured."
    "Every curse has a counter-spell."
    "The spell that remembers everything."

