                     #3  K A Z O N K  (Score: 82/100)

################################################################################
################################################################################

  Say it:    "Ka-ZONK" (fun, impactful, energetic)
  Meaning:   The SOUND of a reminder hitting you. Kazoo + bonk.
  Letters:   6
  Vibe:      Loud, fun, high-energy, impossible to ignore

================================================================================
  THE ORIGIN STORY
================================================================================

  Let's be honest.

  You have ignored every reminder you have ever set. The alarm goes
  off. You swipe it away. The push notification appears. You clear it.
  The to-do app sends a gentle nudge. You pretend you didn't see it.

  Reminders are supposed to REMIND you. But they have become white
  noise. Background static. Furniture.

  KAZONK is not furniture.

  KAZONK is the sound of a reminder that actually LANDS. Not because
  we scream louder -- because we are smarter. AI that knows the
  EXACT moment you need the reminder. The EXACT channel you will
  actually check. The EXACT tone that cuts through the noise.

  WhatsApp at 8 AM when you are reading WhatsApp.
  A Telegram nudge between meetings.
  An Instagram DM with your daily tasks and a Stoic quote.
  And if you STILL ignore it? Escalation. Push -> WhatsApp -> SMS.
  Because KAZONK does not give up on you.

  Some apps whisper. Some apps buzz. KAZONK hits different.

  Built by METAminds. Powered by AI. Delivered with impact.

