================================================================================
  MASCOT & VISUAL IDENTITY
================================================================================

  MASCOT: "Zonk" -- a cartoonish lightning bolt with a face. Crashes
  into frame when reminders fire. Comic-book impact stars around it.
  ENERGETIC, LOUD, IMPOSSIBLE TO IGNORE.
  OR: No mascot. Every notification IS the brand. Comic panels.
  Impact stars. Speed lines. The brand IS the impact.

  COLORS:
    Primary: Electric yellow (#FFD600)
    Secondary: Hot red (#FF1744)
    Accent: Deep black (#000000)
    Style: Comic-book / pop art. Halftone dots. Ben-Day dots.
    Roy Lichtenstein meets app design.

  LOGO: "KAZONK" in bold, tilted comic-book lettering with impact star
  behind the O. K's have speed lines. Everything screams ENERGY.

  ANIMATION:
    Tasks don't appear -- they SLAM into view.
    Completions EXPLODE with confetti.
    Reminders CRASH in with comic-book effects.
    Escalating reminders get MORE dramatic each time.

================================================================================
  SONIC BRANDING
================================================================================

  THIS IS KAZONK'S SUPERPOWER. The notification sound IS the brand.

  Notification: A percussive "KA-ZONK" -- deep bass "KA-" hit +
  bright metallic "ZONK!" clash. Unlike any notification on any phone.
  Hear it across a room. Instantly recognizable.

  Sonic logo: The word itself. "KA-ZONK." Two beats, one brand.

  Task done: Triumphant comic-book "ZING!" -- you defeated the task.

  Escalating reminders:
    1st: gentle *zonk*
    2nd: *KA-zonk*
    3rd: **KA-ZONK!**
    4th: full orchestral **MEGA-KAZONK** with timpani drums

